Maintaining Amount of Cryptocurrency
    instead of burning currency, 90% of total gas on block serves as reward
    10% of total gas goes to creator of currency
Restructuring Gas Fee based on transaction value and Bytes of the message data
    gas fee per transaction = value of message / 1000 + 10 wei per Byte of the message data
    if value of message < 1000 wei charge only 10 wei per Byte of the message data
Reward increase/ decrease with block difficulty
    if block difficulty > 10
        95% of total gas on block serves as reward & 5% of total gas goes to creator of currency
    if block difficulty < 5
        85% of total gas on block serves as reward & 15% of total gas goes to creator of currency
